overview: The user wanted to enhance the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which initially had a generic and uninspired design. The
  agent conducted a detailed aesthetic analysis, identifying areas for
  improvement in color, typography, layout, and form elements. A new, calming
  sleep-themed color palette was introduced, and the main form layout, progress
  indicator, and intro section were redesigned with subtle visual enhancements.
  All core UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders, and cards were
  polished for better user experience. The agent then systematically applied
  consistent styling across all questionnaire sections, replacing old
  gray-bordered boxes with a more refined card-like design. During this process,
  a console error related to  values being passed to input fields was
  identified and fixed by modifying the  component to safely handle such
  values. The overall outcome is a significantly more polished, cohesive, and
  thematically appropriate application, with further minor aesthetic refinements
  planned.
